 img.enlarge  Back to topNews and AnnouncementsAn Evening with Steve Smith Jr to Help Raise Money for KIPP CharlotteKIPP Charlotte was featured on ESPN Live to promote the Evening with Steve Smith Jr event on November 18th.On Tuesday morning, November 5th, Head of Schools for KIPP Charlotte, Anokhi Saraiya, appeared on ESPN Live radio to speak about KIPP Charlotte, the work the region has done to help every student climb the mountain to and through college, and to promote the event "An Evening with Steve Smith Jr."On November 18th, Steve Smith Jr will be presenting at a cocktail party for KIPP Charlotte to speak about his passion for education and helping students and to support the work that KIPP Charlotte has been doing in the community since 2007. All are welcome to purchase tickets to this momentous event and meet the former Panther's player.Tickets are $150 for the event which will take place at the Elder Gallery and Collector's Room from 7:00 - 8:30pm. Ticket price includes a presentation by Steve Smith Jr, an open bar, hors d'oeuvres, a raffle, DJ, and more. Get your tickets here: https://events.r20.constantcontact.com/register/eventReg?oeidk=a07egk6anqfb97cd10e&oseq=&c=&ch=To hear Anokhi Saraiya talk about KIPP's impact and this event, listen to her interview on ESPN Live Radio here: http://www.espncharlotte.net/an-evening-with-steve-smith-to-help-raise-money-for-kipp/https://events.r20.constantcontact.com/regist...KIPP Change Academy (K-4)5431 Hickory Grove RoadCharlotte, NC 28215Phone: (704) 209-9944KIPP Academy Charlotte (5-8)931 Wilann DriveCharlotte, NC 28215Phone: (704) 537-2044KIPP CharlotteFacebookTwitterLinkedinMailpowered by Educational Networks//proxyKiller();var curWindowOnLoad = window.onload;
