 img.enlarge  Back to topNews and AnnouncementsKIPP Charlotte Dancing Lions Step Team featured on Fox46 CharlotteNovember 6th the KIPP Academy Charlotte Dancing Lions Step Team was featured on Fox46 Charlotte News to promote the KIPP Charlotte upcoming event, "An Evening with Steve Smith Sr."This morning, the KIPP Academy Charlotte Dancing Lions Step Team was featured on Fox46 Charlotte News showing off their newest step routine to promote the KIPP Charlotte upcoming event, "An Evening with Steve Smith Sr."The Dancing Lions are just one of the many sports and extra curriculars that KIPP Academy Charlotte offers its students and is led by 5th Grade Math Teacher, Ms. Jerrica Turner. The young women of the Dancing Lions meet several days a week after school, perfecting their routines and learning new steps to cheer on the cross country and basketball teams and compete on a local and state level.To see more of the Dancing Lions, come to "An Evening with Steve Smith Sr" on November 18th at the Elders Gallery and Collectors Room in the South End neighborhood of Charlotte from 7 - 8:30pm. Tickets are $150 per person and include a presentation by Steve Smith Sr, open bar, hors d'oeuvres, a raffle, and more. Come support KIPP Charlotte and our students!Tickets are here: https://events.r20.constantcontact.com/register/eventReg?oeidk=a07egk6anqfb97cd10e&oseq=&c=&ch=https://www.fox46charlotte.com/video/622563KIPP Change Academy (K-4)5431 Hickory Grove RoadCharlotte, NC 28215Phone: (704) 209-9944KIPP Academy Charlotte (5-8)931 Wilann DriveCharlotte, NC 28215Phone: (704) 537-2044KIPP CharlotteFacebookTwitterLinkedinMailpowered by Educational Networks//proxyKiller();var curWindowOnLoad = window.onload;
