 img.enlarge  Back to topNews and AnnouncementsKendra Scott Jewelry will donate 20% of sales to KIPP Charlotte on December 4thTo support KIPP Charlotte students and staff, Kendra Scott Jewelry will be donating 20% of their sales from 6 - 8pm on December 4th.Thank you Kendra Scott Jewelry for supporting KIPP Charlotte during this holiday season! On December 4th from 6 - 8pm 20% of all sales in their Southpark Mall store or over the phone will be given to KIPP Charlotte to help us support our KIPPsters in climbing the mountain to and through college.Kendra Scott Jewelry uses beautiful stones and metals to create unique pieces that are perfect holiday gifts! We are so thankful for their generosity and hope our entire Team and Family take the opportunity to do some holiday shopping while simultaneously supporting our schools.To ensure KIPP Charlotte receives the donation, you can either shop in the Southpark Mall store from 6 - 8pm on December 4th or you can call-in an order to the Southpark Mall store between 6 - 8pm. Both will benefit our schools and KIPPsters!https://www.kendrascott.com/Kendra_Scott_Jewelry_at_Town__County(1.05 MB)KIPP Change Academy (K-4)5431 Hickory Grove RoadCharlotte, NC 28215Phone: (704) 209-9944KIPP Academy Charlotte (5-8)931 Wilann DriveCharlotte, NC 28215Phone: (704) 537-2044KIPP CharlotteFacebookTwitterLinkedinMailpowered by Educational Networks//proxyKiller();var curWindowOnLoad = window.onload;
