 img.enlarge  Back to topNews and AnnouncementsKIPP Teacher Guest on Ellen for Pampering His StudentsAzel Prather, a PreK and Kindergarten KIPP DC teacher was honored on Ellen this week after he teamed up with local hairdressers and barbershops to provide hair and nail services for his students.On February 18, 2020, Azel Prather, a PreK and Kindergarten Teacher with KIPP DC was honored on the Ellen Show.After building relationships with his students and families who are 3 - 5 years old, Mr. Prather realized his students and their families who struggling to find the resources to get their hair done. Recognizing how good a new hairstyle or cut makes people feel, he pulledthe local community together to come into his classroom and provide services for his students.KIPP Charlotte is so proud of Mr. Prather and our sister region, KIPP DC, and wants to send them shine for supporting their families and students.https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4BfhUssdKr8KIPP Change Academy (K-4)5431 Hickory Grove RoadCharlotte, NC 28215Phone: (704) 209-9944KIPP Academy Charlotte (5-8)931 Wilann DriveCharlotte, NC 28215Phone: (704) 537-2044KIPP CharlotteFacebookTwitterLinkedinMailpowered by Educational Networks//proxyKiller();var curWindowOnLoad = window.onload;
